arts.ttl: Brazil 1-0 Paraguay: Player Ratings As the Selecao Qualify for 2026 World Cup
arts.sum: Just when it looked like the hosts would head down the tunnel without getting on the scoresheet, Matheus Cunha played a lovely ball across the face of goal to find Vinícius Júnior, who poked home just his seventh career international goal. Still, Vinícius Júnior’s goal was enough to send Brazil to the 2026 FIFA World Cup .
